{"tags":[{"name":"莫比乌斯反演","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/tags/莫比乌斯反演/","url":"\\async\\tags\\莫比乌斯反演.json","count":6}],"categories":[{"name":"数学","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/categories/数学/","url":"\\async\\categories\\数学.json","count":24}],"url":"\\async\\posts\\2015\\03\\16\\BZOJ-2190[SDOI2008]仪仗队.json","date":1426460971000,"path":{"year":2015,"month":3,"day":16,"name":"BZOJ-2190[SDOI2008]仪仗队"},"title":"BZOJ-2190[SDOI2008]仪仗队","permalink":"http://lzy-foenix.github.io/2015/03/16/BZOJ-2190[SDOI2008]仪仗队/","content":"<hr>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"题解：\"><a href=\"#题解：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题解：\"></a>题解：</h3><p>莫比乌斯反演的一个简单应用，题目就是要求求$\\sum_{i=1}^{n}\\sum_{j=1}^{n}[gcd(i,j)=1]$ 的对数</p>\n<h3 id=\"推导：\"><a href=\"#推导：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"推导：\"></a>推导：</h3><p>定义$f(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}\\sum_{j=1}^{n}[gcd(i,j)=x]$的对数<br>定义$F(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}\\sum_{j=1}^{n}[x|gcd(i,j)]$的对数<br>则变换$F(x)$<br>$$F(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{\\frac{n}{x}}\\sum_{j=1}^{\\frac{n}{x}}[1|gcd(i,j)]$$<br>$$=\\sum_{i=1}^{\\frac{n}{x}}\\sum_{j=1}^{\\frac{n}{x}}1$$<br>$$=[\\frac{n}{x}][\\frac{n}{x}]$$</p>\n<p>由$f(x)$的定义可知 $Ans=f(1)$所以我们利用刚刚推导出的$F(x)$来变换$f(x)$<br>$$f(x)=\\sum_{x|d}^{d}\\mu(\\frac{d}{x})F(d)$$<br>$$=\\sum_{x|d}^{d}\\mu(\\frac{d}{x})[\\frac{N}{d}][\\frac{N}{d}]$$<br>$$Ans=f(1)=\\sum_{d=1}^{n}\\mu(d)[\\frac{N}{d}][\\frac{N}{d}]\\blacksquare$$<br>我们利用分块的思想，先求$\\mu(n)$的前缀和，再$O(n^{1/2})$的来求答案，可对付多组数据的题目。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码：\"><a href=\"#代码：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码：\"></a>代码：</h3><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div><div class=\"line\">7</div><div class=\"line\">8</div><div class=\"line\">9</div><div class=\"line\">10</div><div class=\"line\">11</div><div class=\"line\">12</div><div class=\"line\">13</div><div class=\"line\">14</div><div class=\"line\">15</div><div class=\"line\">16</div><div class=\"line\">17</div><div class=\"line\">18</div><div class=\"line\">19</div><div class=\"line\">20</div><div class=\"line\">21</div><div class=\"line\">22</div><div class=\"line\">23</div><div class=\"line\">24</div><div class=\"line\">25</div><div class=\"line\">26</div><div class=\"line\">27</div><div class=\"line\">28</div><div class=\"line\">29</div><div class=\"line\">30</div><div class=\"line\">31</div><div class=\"line\">32</div><div class=\"line\">33</div><div class=\"line\">34</div><div class=\"line\">35</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> MAXN=<span class=\"number\">50005</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> N,mu[MAXN],prime[MAXN],tot,sum[MAXN],ans;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> not_prime[MAXN];</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">Getmu</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\tmu[<span class=\"number\">1</span>]=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">2</span>;i&lt;=N;i++)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!not_prime[i])&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\tprime[++tot]=i; mu[i]=<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;prime[j]*i&lt;=N;j++)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\tnot_prime[prime[j]*i]=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i%prime[j]==<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tmu[prime[j]*i]=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t\tmu[prime[j]*i]=-mu[i];</div><div class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=N;i++)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tsum[i]=mu[i]; sum[i]+=sum[i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>];</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%lld\"</span>,&amp;N);N--;</div><div class=\"line\">\tGetmu();</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>,last=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;=N;i=last+<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tlast=N/(N/i);</div><div class=\"line\">\t\tans+=(sum[last]-sum[i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])*(N/i)*(N/i);</div><div class=\"line\">\t&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%lld\\n\"</span>,ans+<span class=\"number\">2</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdin</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\tfclose(<span class=\"built_in\">stdout</span>);</div><div class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>"}